            <title>[SPARK-32911] UnsafeExternalSorter.SpillableIterator cannot spill after reading all records</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-32911</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;No memory is freed after calling &lt;tt&gt;UnsafeExternalSorter.SpillableIterator.spill()&lt;/tt&gt; when all records have been read, even though it is still holding onto some memory. This may starve other {{MemoryConsumer}}s of memory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
